ed="T" n="0719c19"/><persName key="A001275">釋智通</persName>，姓<name>趙</name>氏，本<placeName key="PL000000004907"><placeName>陝州</placeName><placeName>安邑</placeName></placeName>人也。<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName><date notBefore-iso="+0605-01-28" key="j19420591946754" notAfter-iso="+0617-12-06"><name>大業</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0719c20"/>出家受具，後隸名<placeName key="PL000000042422">總持寺</placeName>。律行精明，經論該<lb
ed="T" n="0719c21"/>博<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g350"/>。自幼挺秀，即有遊方之志，因往<placeName key="PL000000023589"><placeName>洛京</placeName><placeName>翻<lb
ed="T" n="0719c22"/>經館</placeName></placeName>學<name>梵</name>書并語，曉然明解。屬<date notBefore-iso="+0627-01-26" key="j19500921958507" notAfter-iso="+0650-02-09"><name>貞觀</name>中</date>，有<lb
ed="T" n="0719c23"/><placeName key="PL000000055420">北天竺</placeName>僧齎到《千臂千眼經》<name>梵</name>本，<persName key="A002414">太宗</persName>勅搜<lb
ed="T" n="0719c24"/>天下僧中學解者充<placeName key="PL000000023589">翻經館</placeName>綴文、筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>、證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/><lb
ed="T" n="0719c25"/>等<ptr target="#n176"/>。<persName key="A001275">通</persName>應其選，與<name>梵</name>僧對譯，成二卷<ptr target="#n351"/>。<persName key="A002146">天皇</persName><date from-iso="+0653-02-06" key="j19596001959954" to-iso="+0654-01-26"><name>永<lb
ed="T" n="0719c26"/>徽</name>四年</date>，復於<ref target="#PL000000042422" type="place">本寺</ref>出《千囀陀羅尼觀世音菩<lb
ed="T" n="0719c27"/>薩呪》一卷<ptr target="#n178"/>、《觀自在菩薩隨心呪》一卷<ptr target="#n179"/>、《清淨觀世<lb
ed="T" n="0719c28"/>音菩薩陀羅尼》一卷<ptr target="#n180"/>，共四部五卷。<persName key="A001275">通</persName>善其<name>梵</name><lb
ed="T" n="0719c29"/>字，復究<name>華</name>言，敵對相翻，時皆推伏。又云行<pb ed="T" n="0720a" xml:id="T50.2061.0720a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0720a01"/>瑜伽祕密<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g352"/>教，大有感通。後不知所終。</p>
